node.text:
Happy Earth Day!

Thank you to everyone who shared their amazing creative suggestions with @wyliecaudillart last week. In honor of #EarthMonth, Wylie painted an incredible triple-vignette mural that will certainly impress you. Watch the entire creative process - and tell us what you think of the final reveal!

Should we invite Wylie to paint another mural? If so, comment and share your ideas!

#SHLTR #EarthDay #EarthDay2021

node.text:
Transform your bedroom into a luxurious, cozy suite with these ideas:

1️⃣Add a storage bench at the foot of your bed that combines luxury and utility.

2️⃣Don’t be afraid to layer a rug over your carpet. When layering rugs, either fill the entire space or define a clear zone within a carpeted room.

3️⃣Place crown molding along the top of the wall where it meets the ceiling to give it a high-end appearance. 

4️⃣Incorporate metallic touches in your furniture or decor - but don’t overdo it.

🚨For more #SHLTRInsider tips, check out our web series with design pro @johngidding on YouTube! Link to our most recent episode can be found in our bio.

#SHLTR
